Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,==================================TITLE
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.78,0:00:08.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,送给被杀害的占卜师罗珊的请柬
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.61,0:00:12.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,箱庭之夜
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.02,0:00:16.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然一时心血来潮来到了这里
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.55,0:00:19.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过这样真的好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.91,0:00:24.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,引路的人在我们上船之后就消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.85,0:00:28.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂...喂 维多利加!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.85,0:00:34.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 久城
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.26,0:00:35.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然只顾自己吃 太狡猾了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.06,0:00:37.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的肚子也很饿啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.24,0:00:43.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我们是凭着罗珊的请柬来的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.48,0:00:46.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以晚餐也只有一人份
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.93,0:00:49.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉 算了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.98,0:00:52.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去找点别的东西吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.55,0:00:55.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有带什么点心来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.68,0:01:01.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的头脑所指示出的必要的道具
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.02,0:01:05.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紧急食品套装 也在那些道具之中
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.41,0:01:10.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它们都被留在了学园里
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.35,0:01:13.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成为了你强词夺理的牺牲品
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.27,0:01:16.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这是自作自受
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.45,0:01:18.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么强词夺理...!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.95,0:01:20.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有什么资格说...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.71,0:01:24.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面包的话 给你这个强词夺理的人倒也可以
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.73,0:01:31.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...真好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.08,0:03:23.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一弥!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.06,0:03:26.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一弥!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.93,0:03:28.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,站起来 一弥!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.17,0:03:37.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,日本男儿 就应习得保护弱者的力量!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.91,0:03:40.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你可是帝国军人的三儿子啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.96,0:03:42.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,站起来 一弥!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.24,0:03:44.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一弥!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.70,0:03:46.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 叫你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.24,0:03:50.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这个喜欢清算物品又满口歪理的留学生
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.41,0:03:52.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我起来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.87,0:03:56.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用你说...我也会起来啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.73,0:04:01.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦...这里是哪里?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.86,0:04:04.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来用餐似乎已经结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.52,0:04:08.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,醒来之后 所有的人就都在这个大厅里了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.20,0:04:14.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里 这里是...哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.58,0:04:15.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,门打不开!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.75,0:04:22.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 怎么回事!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.97,0:04:29.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,痛! 什么嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.11,0:04:32.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久城 有件事很奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.44,0:04:33.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.68,0:04:37.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才在餐厅里还有9个人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.50,0:04:40.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加上我们就是11人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.69,0:04:43.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 现在却有12个人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.11,0:04:47.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多了一个人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.47,0:04:50.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\fn方正姚体\2c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}第2话 死者之魂推动遇难船
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.04,0:04:54.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错 真的有12个人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.20,0:04:56.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是说
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.41,0:05:00.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有个没在餐厅里出现过的人混了进来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.89,0:05:04.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是那个人把昏睡的我们搬到了这里
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.38,0:05:06.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个人为什么要这么做?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.96,0:05:07.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,箱庭吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.97,0:05:10.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,似乎是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.57,0:05:13.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么说来 「野兔」就是那些孩子们了?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.51,0:05:21.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.11,0:05:24.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,QueenBerry号吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.18,0:05:28.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像有点印象啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.81,0:05:30.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别碰那个东西!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.39,0:05:39.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这艘船 果然是...!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.18,0:05:42.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊啊 不会错的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.50,0:05:44.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你没事吧 久城
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.14,0:05:46.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.86,0:05:49.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在图书馆里读到过
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.54,0:05:51.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是鬼故事!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.49,0:05:58.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,QueenBerry号是沉没于十年前的船
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.11,0:06:01.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死者的灵魂不得安宁
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.79,0:06:03.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每当暴风雨之夜它便会出现
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.40,0:06:08.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,引诱生者上船作为活祭品 然后再次沉没
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.28,0:06:15.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你 你那是什么反应啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.85,0:06:19.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我以为你是在讲笑话 所以配合你一下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.19,0:06:21.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 我是很认真地...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.51,0:06:23.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.62,0:06:23.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,停电?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.55,0:06:24.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事 喂
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.31,0:06:26.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,维 维多利加?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.09,0:06:26.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,灯呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.14,0:06:26.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.73,0:06:28.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,维多利加! 你在哪?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.05,0:06:28.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}快开灯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.79,0:06:35.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,维多利加!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.73,0:06:40.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在干什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.54,0:06:42.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.05,0:06:45.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 不 那个...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.67,0:06:50.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.55,0:06:54.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才应该还没有这些字啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.30,0:07:00.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「十年时光已逝 真是白驹过隙」
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.82,0:07:03.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「这一次轮到你们了」
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.21,0:07:05.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「箱子已经备下」
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.69,0:07:12.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「来吧 野兔们 奔跑吧！」
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.45,0:07:17.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,箱庭之夜...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.52,0:07:18.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,野兔...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.60,0:07:23.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「野兔追逐赛」可不是什么有趣的事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.55,0:07:26.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们...才是野兔啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.24,0:07:31.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会被那些孩子们杀掉的!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.35,0:07:33.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没用的 那扇门上了锁...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.31,0:07:43.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那 那扇门已经安全了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.78,0:07:44.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快逃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.94,0:07:46.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,陷阱已经解除了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.96,0:07:48.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走 速度快
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.01,0:07:53.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们 你们也快逃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.49,0:07:54.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是...是!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.84,0:08:01.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没 没事的 维多利加
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.36,0:08:03.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟在我后面...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.72,0:08:06.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,维多利加?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.95,0:08:09.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使有人横尸在眼前
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.73,0:08:12.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她似乎也完全不在意啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.21,0:08:16.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等 等等我!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.31,0:08:25.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们要用救生艇吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.21,0:08:28.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然在这么汹涌的海上用救生艇
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.54,0:08:29.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太危险了!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.98,0:08:31.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 大叔!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.52,0:08:32.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放 放开我!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.99,0:08:35.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,留在这艘船上 就要沦为野兔了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.98,0:08:37.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要放下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.39,0:08:39.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 等等啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.73,0:08:42.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要丢下我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.19,0:08:44.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这也太乱来了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.57,0:09:06.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可...可恶啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.86,0:09:11.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都警告过你们了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.88,0:09:15.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结束了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.54,0:09:23.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么多人死去 维多利加却还...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.50,0:09:28.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回忆起了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.34,0:09:31.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,植物园里的维多利加
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.00,0:09:33.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,洋娃娃般的维多利加
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.08,0:09:38.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神秘而不可思议
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.15,0:09:43.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,维多利加 你究竟是...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.32,0:09:47.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,休伊!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.58,0:09:52.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 他已经死了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.81,0:10:07.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我受不了了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.43,0:10:08.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.96,0:10:16.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们只不过去了趟甲板...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.31,0:10:19.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 尸体哪去了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.81,0:10:21.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,消失了?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.92,0:10:22.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是幽灵...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.97,0:10:27.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们 野兔们回来了!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.23,0:10:29.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 你没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.08,0:10:33.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请喝水
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.30,0:10:37.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 我语无伦次了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.62,0:10:48.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫莫里斯 在苏瓦尔外交部工作
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.80,0:10:49.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.63,0:10:54.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朱莉·盖尔 ...无业
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.81,0:10:58.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我父亲拥有一座煤矿
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.91,0:11:04.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫涅德·巴格斯塔 在英国从事话剧演员的职业
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.00,0:11:06.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正好要在下个月的公演里...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.63,0:11:10.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,饰演杀人犯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.42,0:11:12.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该 该不会是你...!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.73,0:11:13.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.90,0:11:15.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那 那个
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.74,0:11:18.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是来自日本的久城一弥
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.06,0:11:20.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接着 这位是...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.34,0:11:22.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她叫维多利加
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.20,0:11:24.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,维多利加?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.21,0:11:28.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恕我冒昧 我们是不是见过面呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.29,0:11:32.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莫里斯 你是不是该向乘上这艘船的年轻人们
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.14,0:11:34.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将来龙去脉解释清楚呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.94,0:11:38.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你 你在说什...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.04,0:11:39.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那艘船模
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.75,0:11:44.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当我的朋友正试图去触摸那艘船模时
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.47,0:11:46.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你向他发出了警告
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.59,0:11:48.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你为什么会知道那个机关
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.73,0:11:57.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 我认得这艘船
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.95,0:12:01.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为 这艘船正是十年前
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.31,0:12:09.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,1914年沉没在这片地中海里的QueenBerry号
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.50,0:12:17.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,过去 这艘船上载着被称为野兔的孩子们
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.01,0:12:23.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发色 瞳色和语言都不相同
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.23,0:12:26.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来自于世界各地的十一名少年少女
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.06,0:12:31.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因成年人的某种目的而被选中的他们
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.24,0:12:35.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这艘QueenBerry号上度过了一夜
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.18,0:12:39.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天亮以后
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.75,0:12:43.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我受上司之命调查了这艘船
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.28,0:12:45.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结果...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.71,0:12:47.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,孩子们怎么了?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.96,0:12:49.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们死了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.65,0:12:52.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死于自相残杀
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.15,0:12:56.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「某个目的」究竟是什么!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.93,0:12:58.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么孩子们会...!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.19,0:13:02.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是收回遗体罢了 详细情况我也不知道!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.61,0:13:07.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 他们为什么会自相残杀
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.83,0:13:09.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这我也不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.90,0:13:14.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,船舱不断进水 这艘船就这么沉没了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.91,0:13:18.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你所知的鬼故事就是发源于此的 久城
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.22,0:13:22.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幽灵船QueenBerry号
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.95,0:13:26.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死者们的灵魂将遇难船推上了海面
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.39,0:13:30.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自那天起过了整整十年
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.94,0:13:36.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为他们带去死亡的成人们被集中起来 然后死去...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.17,0:13:41.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一切都完了 我们也会死的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.11,0:13:47.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶 你又这么笑
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.78,0:13:48.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什 什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.94,0:13:50.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么好笑的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.28,0:13:53.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是在配合你的笑话
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.61,0:13:55.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笑话? 我可是...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.50,0:14:00.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幽灵会写请柬 你觉得这可能吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.93,0:14:02.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的确...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.73,0:14:06.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可 可是 这艘船的确沉入了海底
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.53,0:14:10.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们能不能用鼻子闻闻呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.41,0:14:15.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这股气味是...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.17,0:14:18.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚刚涂上的油漆的味道
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.03,0:14:20.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有这葡萄酒
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.29,0:14:25.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从标签上来看 是1890年产
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.61,0:14:31.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,酿造于30多年前的苏瓦尔红酒
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.19,0:14:34.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 它的色泽却还很鲜艳
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.73,0:14:36.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,香气也很新鲜
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.68,0:14:37.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.65,0:14:41.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这瓶酒的酿造厂
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.34,0:14:47.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经毁于1914年夏季爆发的世界大战的战火之中
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.15,0:14:50.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样的酒早已买不到了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.66,0:14:52.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么说来 标签...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.40,0:14:54.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恐怕是重新贴上的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.03,0:14:57.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么要特地这么做呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.47,0:14:58.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还用问吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.03,0:15:02.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然是为了完全再现原来的那艘船啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.22,0:15:03.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可 可是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.13,0:15:04.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,墙壁上的那面血书
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.32,0:15:07.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这间浸水的大厅
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.29,0:15:09.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有尸体又消失到哪去了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.52,0:15:14.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与其我多费口舌
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.79,0:15:19.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不如用让你们都能看到的方式 重组混沌的碎片吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.63,0:15:25.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当我们从甲板回来的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.12,0:15:28.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,理所当然地进入了现在所在的房间
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.25,0:15:29.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但这是为什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.94,0:15:31.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为门开着啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.09,0:15:33.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其他房间的门都关着
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.16,0:15:35.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正是如此
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.66,0:15:36.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 久城
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.88,0:15:39.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你把那扇门打开
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.01,0:15:48.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.73,0:15:53.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 这边也有刚才的大厅...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.97,0:15:59.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们最初所在的是这个房间
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.76,0:16:02.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这只是个很简单的圈套
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.88,0:16:04.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有这墙上的血书
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.79,0:16:08.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我重组混沌碎片所得到的结论
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.57,0:16:11.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,导出的答案 就是这个
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.18,0:16:14.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,壁...纸?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.65,0:16:15.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.36,0:16:22.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将贴在预先写好的文字上的壁纸一口气揭下来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.93,0:16:26.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这点动作在停电的空隙里已经足以完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.78,0:16:29.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来是这样 知道方法以后就很简单了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.71,0:16:32.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害 你果然好厉害啊 维多利加
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.74,0:16:33.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘘
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.20,0:16:37.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水声
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.99,0:16:44.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 进水了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.74,0:16:47.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快到无线电室去求救!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.31,0:16:51.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们还在磨蹭什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.14,0:16:54.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想和船一起沉入海底吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.72,0:16:58.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果这艘船是QueenBerry号
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.88,0:17:02.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么要想到达无线电室 就必须先往下走一趟
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.27,0:17:06.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 这艘船的构造怎么这么麻烦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.96,0:17:09.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 是电梯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.11,0:17:10.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,站住!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.63,0:17:17.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去找楼梯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.45,0:17:26.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,维多利加 来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.15,0:17:32.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是...什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.30,0:17:35.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶 因为很危险啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.65,0:17:36.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把手给我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.52,0:17:41.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久城 我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.72,0:17:44.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一被你指责就会特别生气啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.79,0:17:46.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我 我只是担心你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.06,0:17:48.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说的算什么话嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.50,0:17:50.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这好强的乖僻女
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.91,0:17:51.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.13,0:18:02.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然连这种地方都有陷阱...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.39,0:18:06.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 各位 楼梯就在前面
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.18,0:18:20.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你很温柔呢 少年
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.07,0:18:26.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才不也拼命保护了那位女孩吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.31,0:18:28.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我 我也没做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.71,0:18:31.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是个男子汉大丈夫呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.33,0:18:38.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她只是看到我们牵手的样子罢了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.05,0:18:40.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧 久城
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.00,0:18:47.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.23,0:18:49.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这下全完了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.06,0:18:52.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 快走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.94,0:18:55.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,动作快点应该还来得及
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.31,0:18:57.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.12,0:19:02.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上 上来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.81,0:19:07.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点 快到我背上来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.39,0:19:08.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没时间犹豫了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.04,0:19:14.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,维多利加
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.30,0:19:17.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你 你勒到我的脖子了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.57,0:19:18.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忍着吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.01,0:19:20.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要啊 会死人的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.44,0:19:24.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是你自己选择背负的累赘
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.17,0:19:28.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,累赘?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.36,0:19:33.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别说累赘了 这重量还不如旅行箱呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.73,0:19:37.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女孩子是这么轻的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.01,0:19:44.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,维多利加...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.47,0:19:48.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你该不会是害怕吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.60,0:19:50.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.32,0:19:53.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.05,0:19:55.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.09,0:19:58.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论如何聪明
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.60,0:20:01.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论如何乖僻
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.37,0:20:04.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,维多利加毕竟是个女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.00,0:20:08.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是个娇小的 娇小的女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.08,0:20:13.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原本 带她来旅行的人就是我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.29,0:20:15.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.31,0:20:21.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,日本男儿 就应习得保护弱者的力量!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.11,0:20:28.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们看 从这里好像能上到安全地带
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.65,0:20:32.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行了 再这样下去会变成野兔的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.90,0:20:34.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,振作点
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.27,0:20:36.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是为了不落到那种地步 才要到无线电室去的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.78,0:20:38.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果没人来救援怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.07,0:20:41.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,横竖都要死的话 不如拉你们垫背
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.93,0:20:44.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你突然间干什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.59,0:20:45.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.09,0:20:51.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大叔 你适可而止啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.11,0:20:58.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这艘船上藏着很多武器
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.86,0:21:03.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抽屉里 花瓶里 地毯下 到处都是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.15,0:21:05.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是为了什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.55,0:21:07.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了让他们自相残杀啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.07,0:21:12.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,野兔们受到猎犬挑拨 开始互相怀疑
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.85,0:21:16.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当他们发现武器之后 便开始自相残杀!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.45,0:21:17.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,猎犬?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.97,0:21:20.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来吧 你们谁是野兔
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.03,0:21:22.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,野兔都死了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.89,0:21:23.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吵死了!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.61,0:21:26.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也有人活了下来
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.53,0:21:29.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙现在正好就和你们差不多大
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.03,0:21:34.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经什么都不知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.06,0:21:35.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 我要把你们全都杀光
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.85,0:21:38.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,独自从这艘船里逃出去!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.90,0:21:41.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莫里斯先生
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.24,0:21:44.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这事和维多利加没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.74,0:21:47.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,关系? 那种东西无所谓
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.82,0:21:49.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愚蠢的人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.30,0:21:59.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我 我绝不允许...你这么做!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.61,0:22:02.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久城...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.13,0:22:05.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在干什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.84,0:22:08.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我邀你来的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.90,0:22:12.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作为帝国军人的三儿子
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.86,0:22:15.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我必须保证维多利加你活着回去
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.15,0:22:18.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有这样的责任!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.36,0:22:24.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗 是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.17,0:22:26.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就是野兔吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.97,0:22:28.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你就去死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.58,0:24:07.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,野兔和...猎犬?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.27,0:24:10.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 我什么都不知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.23,0:24:14.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让人难以理解的还有你 久城
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.75,0:24:18.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么你会如此为相识不久的我着想...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.47,0:24:18.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}下回 野兔们在朝阳下许下约定